Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世之初 冥冥之中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the beginning there was darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着一声爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了无尽膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天 新的发现都在揭秘这个诡异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking the mysterious,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼 神秘莫测的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the mind-blowing, the deadly secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方 - 我们所谓的《宇宙》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是宇宙的怪胎 -\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They are the freaks of the cosmos--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脉冲星与类星体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}pulsars and quasars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们怪异到连生存都似乎不大可能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So strange, their very existence seems impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们必须是巨人 十足的怪兽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They must be titanic, absolute monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么让它们发出十亿个太阳的光辉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What makes them shine with the light of a billion suns,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋转比眨眼都快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}rotate faster than the blink of an eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或爆发出的宇宙节奏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or bang out cosmic rhythms
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与《感恩而死》的鼓手一般？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with the drummer from The Grateful Dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我开始全身心投入\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Once all of these things started to come my way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就意识到 知道吗 宇宙在欢唱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I realized that, you know, the universe was singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而那是个怪得离奇的曲调\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But it's a tune bizarre beyond imagination,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为脉冲星与类星体 -\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with pulsars and quasars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文插曲的超级明星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the superstars of an astronomical sideshow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能出现在宇宙最怪异的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}found only in the strangest sectors of the universe.
